5:41 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Faction reset!!!</span><hr size=1> # I petitioned the GMs and they pretty much told me I was FoS. They said that I could have altered my faction this way on purpose.  #<br>
<br>
And this is a steaming pile of horse manure as well, not to mention incredibly stupid, because there's NO WAY you can &quot;alter your faction that way on purpose&quot;.<br>
<br>
It is functionally IMPOSSIBLE for any player who has played the game for a while to bring himself back to &quot;base faction&quot; with all faction groups.  Some factions can only go one direction (just *try* to raise your BurynaLegion faction after you've lowered it by killing any Burynai, there's absolutely no in-game action that raises that faction), and others can't be altered without simultaneously changing other factions (e.g., kill a GFay/Crushbone Orc and your IndigoBrotherhood faction goes down, whereas ALL methods of raising that faction will damage various wood elf or halfling factions).<br>
<br>
Keep pounding on them until you get escalated to someone who has an ounce of sense.  If nothing else, email Brad McQuaid, he has participated on several discussions on the Usenet Everquest newsgroup, and really comes across as a reasonable guy. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showMessage?topicID=11929.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showMessage?topicID=11830.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=11913.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.threadControl?topicID=11913.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11913.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11913.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="paladinsofnorrathgeneral">General<option value="paladinsofnorrathholyswordsandquests">Holy Swords and Quests<option value="paladinsofnorrathfrm8">Epic Quests<option value="paladinsofnorrathfrm9">Paladin Polls<op